{"tid":1610252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我老豆話你地失曬焦","createTime":"2019-10-01T16:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T18:17:23.000Z","uid":307620,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6ef67c9e37f244deef542c972e71670277ca20b7","tid":1610252,"uid":307620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:50:10.000Z","msg":"佢話唔應該搞黨鐵<br />\n話破壞嘅都係死物<br />\n黨鐵唔會回應亦都回應唔到五大訴求<br />\n又話唔應該搞狗仔<br />\n話咩佢地係失控係情有可原<br />\n狗仔都唔會亦都回應唔到五大訴求<br />\n話要搞就搞政府部門<br />\n癱瘓部門阻礙政府運作<br />\n先可以有效咁逼到政府回應五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n佢講嘅嘢不無道理<br />\n但係聽到話狗仔情有可原嗰陣立即燥咗<br />\n屌你射到人就死都情有可原？<br />\n<br />\nbtw 想知大家點睇<br />\nsor for P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463dc739b400074ab4c17e2365a2f1c7acd28690","tid":1610252,"uid":307620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:51:11.000Z","msg":"講多句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"a51ee5985fb57ca724d99ff882eee974df788b1b","tid":1610252,"uid":71140,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:51:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8d4b5dbb7caa15149ddb403a9ad42860477d85e","tid":1610252,"uid":288027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a51ee5985fb57ca724d99ff882eee974df788b1b","tid":1610252,"uid":71140,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:51:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01fc19e897376b4366d96c3361744a7a3626408b","tid":1610252,"uid":93395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"好好笑<br />\n<br />\n咁樣乜柒都唔使做啦"},{"pid":"97289509ddfde743a3129f0af857235a5dcbc88d","tid":1610252,"uid":63864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:56:36.000Z","msg":"如果咁講，我地應該係返大陸抗爭先岩？"},{"pid":"7c180c665ff3ef55c6ae1094e607e698bce16fbf","tid":1610252,"uid":102475,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:58:19.000Z","msg":"叫你老豆出黎帶領大家嘛<br />\n講有咩做得唔好好容易<br />\n不如帶頭做d實質具體可行既行動仲好"},{"pid":"d0d16265765f0854ea188375501c4ae77e29a022","tid":1610252,"uid":321626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:59:20.000Z","msg":"你老豆叫你早啲訓"},{"pid":"3c928a9cfced621846422890f0d0f20b414ffa7c","tid":1610252,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:00:28.000Z","msg":"叫你嗌香港獨立都炸哂形咁對咩政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cf7c2304295a6bc72c7e8da335bbc4ed6a487f","tid":1610252,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=2a95c94d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32950016be7aed4869a946f250048b71a07f0580","tid":1610252,"uid":54938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:02:31.000Z","msg":"唔好嘈，咩都要做"},{"pid":"0c1945bda6f762ffe1d8b295a709ef37f38cb0db","tid":1610252,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:03:24.000Z","msg":"講還講，唔好將呢個post推上去"},{"pid":"71edaa60ef2f28b30a687b756bbb2faa3b1c7a14","tid":1610252,"uid":270956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:05:35.000Z","msg":"政總、中聯辦唔叫對準政權？<br />\n政府就係依靠黑警、黨鐵嚟維持政權<br />\n黑警用武力對付示威者<br />\n黨鐵運兵俾黑警入站拉人、封站唔俾示威者走<br />\n一日唔打倒黑警、黨鐵，<br />\n一日無可能打贏政權"},{"pid":"22c1fd76b543eb2a52143127445894a8d4d7940e","tid":1610252,"uid":69754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:06:37.000Z","msg":"諗下黨鐵做過啲咩<br />\n再問佢有無失焦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5784e0432988b75d3d46aabf0b20254952fa0c","tid":1610252,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"經常見到有黑警由黨鐵辨公室出出入入非常配合"},{"pid":"f8d6b325bc246a93fd106d458566bf5da2b07f7c","tid":1610252,"uid":103363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:12:58.000Z","msg":"係成個政府乃至所有有關嘅公營機構都要搞"},{"pid":"e45647c9d962d444dcd31d14851a92ce9fde0ea2","tid":1610252,"uid":307620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a51ee5985fb57ca724d99ff882eee974df788b1b","tid":1610252,"uid":71140,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:51:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:37:09.000Z","msg":"我18 我老豆今年過咗60大壽"},{"pid":"e5bc91c85dd260ba3300e920becf178ff402bcc9","tid":1610252,"uid":307620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01fc19e897376b4366d96c3361744a7a3626408b","tid":1610252,"uid":93395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"好好笑<br />\n<br />\n咁樣乜柒都唔使